# RawrXD v3.0 - Complete Network Implementation & System Integration

## Critical Analysis of Current Implementation

The provided `net_impl_win32.cpp` contains **simulated network operations** with these critical gaps:
- **No SSL/TLS** (HTTPS impossible)
- **No connection pooling** (performance bottleneck)
- **No timeout handling** (infinite blocking risk)
- **No authentication** (API keys impossible)
- **No error recovery** (crashes on network failure)
- **No resource management** (handle leaks)
- **No thread safety** (race conditions)
- **No logging** (debugging impossible)

---

## Complete Production-Ready Implementation

### 1. `net_impl_win32.h` - Production Network Stack
```cpp
#pragma once
#include <windows.h>
#include <wininet.h>
#include <winsock2.h>
#include <ws2tcpip.h>
#include <string>
